body.name: BAGSMART Carry On Luggage 22x14x9 Airline Approved With TSA Lock, 1OO% Polycarbonate Hardside Luggage with Spinner Wheels, Durable Hard Shell Carry On Suitcase 20 inch Black
features: Airline Approved Luggage: Dimensions: 21.7 x 14 x 8.7 in (wheel and handle height included). Volume: 35 L. Weight: 6.39 lbs. The 20" carry-on luggage size is designed to meet the airline requirements for most major airlines as a carry-on suitcase that can be placed in the overhead bin of almost any flight, anywhere in the world. No more paying for temporary consignments.

Lightweight Yet Durable: The outer shell is made of 1OO% polycarbonate which is an extremely strong yet lightweight and scratch-resistant material that makes the hard shell suitcase look like a new one year after year. The sleek good looks make this an excellent choice for business travelers and those who like to travel in style.

Room For More: BAGSMART hard case suitcase is designed to fit more into your trip. The 2 main compartments of travel luggage with compression cross straps store all your clothes and belongings and keep clothing wrinkle-free, items neatly in place. Individual built-in small pocket is for small items. Generously sized, thoughtfully placed designs maximize every inch of storage, meaning you can get more out of every trip with your carry-on.

All In The Details: A sturdy 4-stage retractable high-grade aluminum tubes handle that offers multiple height positions. The main compartment is protected by a TSA-approved combination lock for extra safety. Move smoother than ever before with newly designed 360° spinner wheels to ensure a smooth ride. To ensure the highest level of quality and durability, we put our products and materials through thousands of experimental tests. Production of 20 inch carry on luggage, we mean it!

Premium Service And Warranty: BAGSMART will back each piece of tsa approved carry on luggage with a 2-year manufacturer's warranty. Before shipment, hard side luggage with spinner wheels undergoes thousands of rigorous tests to ensure that our carry on suitcase meets strict standards and can withstand any journey. If there is any quality problem, please feel free to contact us. Professional and patient customer service will reply to your satisfaction in time.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Why we insist on 100% polycarbonate material? And why choose 100% polycarbonate luggage? Durability: Polycarbonate luggage is known for its strength and durability, making it ideal for travel. Compared with other materials, its high strength can ensure that it can withstand certain impact, pressure, scratches, and other forms of wear and tear during use. Ensuring that it can last for many trips to come.Lightweight: Polycarbonate luggage is lightweight, making it easy to maneuver and carry around. This is especially important for travelers who need to pack a lot of items but want to avoid the hassle of carrying heavy luggage.Security: Polycarbonate suitcase has high impact resistance, which can effectively protect the luggage from damage. Even under heavy pressure or collision, the carry on suitcase can keep its shape and integrity well.Waterproof: Polycarbonate carry on luggage has excellent water resistance, so even in rainy days or other wet environments, the luggage can remain dry.Stylish: Polycarbonate luggage is stylish and durable, not easy to scratch, deformation and other problems, and you can also choose different colors to make your luggage more personalized. In summary, 100% Polycarbonate luggage is an excellent choice for travelers who are looking for a durable, lightweight, and stylish option for their travels.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 2, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Bought this for my husband because I was looking for a carryon bag that met the airline size limits for carryon bags. This bag does that. It is also light and sturdy. Strongly recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 10, 2024
reviews.reviewText: It’s lightweight, runs well and holds an amazing amount. Great for a long weekend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 12, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great carry-on for travel
reviews.reviewText: Great product, it's lined on the interior to protect your belongings and has a strap on one side to secure clothing. Enough pockets to hold my larger toiletries (hairbrush, toothbrush, etc...) The locking mechanism is great, seems very durable. I gave this 4 out of 5 stars only because the case is listed as scratch resistant and I already have some white marks on it after a single trip, I thought it would be a little more durable against this. Outside shell is overall very good and protects your belongings. Pop-up handle works well and it's easy to use. I would definitely buy another product from this company, these seem very well made.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Wheels like a dream so smooth. Great bag! My regular more expensive bag had to be sent in for repair and I purchased this bag to fill in and was so surprised I like it more.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 20, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Worked like it should, nothing broke , and no issues at airport

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 14, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Do not purchase
reviews.reviewText: Stay away from this product.It did not even last one trip.Worked and performed well on the journey out.Packed and headed home after not touching the bag fir a week. Arrived at my seat and the telescoping handle would not go down the final step. So I was standing there in the seat row pounding away at the handle and pushing the button while an entire plane load of people paraded past me. I tried opening the case and accessing the handle from the inside, to no avail. My next move was to flip it upside down and position the case between the seats with the exposed handle on the floor of the cabin.I shoved, and pushed and even jumped on top of the case.Everyone boarding the plane was having a good laugh. My final solution was to just break off the telescoping handle and shove it between my seat and the wall of the cabin, throw this bag in the overhead for my Eight hour flight across the Pacific.If you enjoy looking like a fool in front of a plane full of people this piece is for you.Just avoid this product, it is a sad piece.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and eye catching
reviews.reviewText: I hate flying, pulling luggage and trying to find my luggage. This one I can lock but TSA can unlock when they need too. Eye catching for me to see among all the other bags if needed. I have not used yet but I felt I did something special for me with buying this item.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars True 22 x 14 x 9 Spinner Carry-On
reviews.reviewText: I wanted a true 22 x 14 x 9, spinner, carry-on luggage. I didn't want to mess around with a bag that was slightly larger than the requirements and be told to check it. Like me, you may be finding that most carry-on spinners are a little too big in at least 1 dimension. LOOK NO MORE!This is a great bag. It's made of polycarbonate, so it's strong and very light. It's balanced and doesn't tip over. It rolls great! It has compartments and zippers but also doesn't waste any space. It also features a reprogramable TSA lock.I've traveled with it 3 times now and love it.It's perfect. Buy it.
